Feature: Share Reviews with Google Plus

  
  Scenario: As normal user from the detailed review page
    Given User is on login page
    When User login with "admin1_user" and "admin1_password"
    And User clicks on "Insight_Tab"
    And User clicks on "Reviews_Tab"
    And User select values "Twitter" in "source_dropdown" and apply
    And User clicks on "Details_button" present on Review page
    And User clicks on "Share_Google" present on Review page
    And User switch window
    And User fills in "Google_Email" with "selcywebdriver@gmail.com" present on Review page
    And User clicks on "Google_Next" present on Review page
    And User fills in "Google_Password" with "selcywebdriver44" present on Review page
    And User clicks on "Google_submit" present on Review page
    Then User clicks on "Google_Share_Review" present on Review page